title: David Bowie + Nine Inch Nails - Maryland Heights, MO - 1995-10-1
description:
The Outside Tour with David Bowie and Nine Inch Nails co-headlining, opened on September 14, 1995 at Meadows Music Theatre - Hartford, CT. In a 2012 Rolling Stone reader's poll, the tour (pairing Nine Inch Nails with Bowie) was named one of the top 10 opening acts in rock history.


Nine Inch Nails and David Bowie
Outside Tour
Live at the Riverport Amphitheatre
Maryland Heights, MO
October 11, 1995


Unofficial Mono Soundboard Recording - Excellent Audio Quality
